lectricity infrastructure industry port and industrial estate epc engineering procurement and construction services information technology and medical services hospital the company produces products for both the domestic and the international market on  november  krakatau steel listed  percent of its shares on the indonesia stock exchange idx through an initial public offering ipo krakatauposco steel plant in october  the construction of the krakatauposco steel plant was started this plant that is expected to produce three million tons of steel per year is established as a joint venture between krakatau steel and posco the worlds thirdlargest steelmaker based in south korea and is located in cilegon banten the first phase will be completed by the end of  construction of the plant should be completed in  while production is projected to start in  posco controls a  percent stake in this joint venture the second phase of the production will enlarge production capacity by another three million metric tons of steel thus total production will become six million metric tons per year the second phase of the project will begin at the end of  total investment amounts to usd  billion krakatau steels financial highlights                                 net revenues             gross profit loss                           net income                       operating profit                          profit before tax loss                       total assets             total liabilities               earnings per share¹               in million us dollar unless otherwise stated¹ in us dollarsource krakatau steel annual report  location contact detailsjalan industri no  po box  cilegonbanten  phone    fax    email corseckrakatausteelcomwwwkrakatausteelcom share related pages indonesian steel producers urge govt to monitor imports better july  chinese investors to build carbon steel plant in indonesia june  steel production indonesia government targets  growth in  may  steel producers i